        <address><p><a href="mailto:shaferdp@vmi.edu" title="Deneise Shafer">Deneise Shafer</a><br> Administrative Assistant</p> <p>&nbsp;<a target="_blank" title="facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/VMI-Department-of-History/1613681962191979?ref=hl"><img border="0" src="/uploadedImages/Images/icons/facebook.png?n=469" alt="facebook" title="facebook"></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/VMIHistoryDept" title="twitter" target="_blank"><img border="0" src="/uploadedImages/Images/icons/twitter.png?n=8365" alt="twitter" title="twitter"></a><br><br> P: (540) 464-7338<br> F: (540) 464-7246</p> <p>Virginia Military Institute<br> 536 Scott Shipp Hall<br> Lexington, VA&nbsp; 24450</p> <p><a href="mailto:shaferdp@vmi.edu">Contact History</a></p> </address> 
