        <li>Reuter, T., "The End of the Carolingian Military Expansion," in P. Goodman and R. Collins (eds) <em>Charlemagne’s Heir: New Perspectives on the Reign of Louis the Pious</em> (814-40), Oxford: The Clarendon Press, 1990, pp. 391-405.</li> 
        <li>Reuter, T., "Carolingian and Ottonian Warfare," in M. Keen (ed.) <em>Medieval Warfare: A History, Oxford</em>: Oxford University Press, 1999, pp. 13-35.</li> 
