       <p><strong>VIKINGS</strong></p> 
       <ul> 
        <li>Clark, H.B., "The Vikings," in M. Keen ed. <em>Medieval Warfare</em>, pp. 36-58.</li> 
        <li>Coupland, S., "Charles the Bald and the Defense of the West Frankish Kingdom against the Viking Invasions 846-77," <em>Ph.D. Dissertation</em>, Cambridge University, 1987.</li> 
        <li>Fernandex-Armesto, F., "Naval Warfare after the Viking Age c. 1100-1500," in M. Keen (ed) <em>Medieval Warfare: A History, Oxford</em>, 1999, pp. 230-252.</li> 
