        <li>Smail, R.C., <em>Crusading Warfare 1097-1193</em>. ed. C. Marshall, Cambridge: Cambridge University Press, 1992.</li> 
       </ul> 
      </div> 
      <div id="ctl00_pageContent_rightColumn"> 
       <div id="content-2" class="column last"> 
        <div id="ctl00_pageContent_relatedRight10737427402" class="mod"> 
